Brady Boone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brady_Boone 0 Dean R. Peters (August 22, 1958 – December 15, 1998) was an American professional wrestler and referee. He was perhaps best known for his appearances with the World Wrestling Federation under the ring names Brady Boone and Battle Kat.
